classic-hello-world-python-sdk.title: Classic Hello World! Python SDK
classic-hello-world-python-sdk.desc:
Get started with a classic Hello World! example.
	This example executes foo(), bar(), and baz() in an await chain pattern.
	Each function appends to the greeting.
	This example does NOT require the use of a Resonate Server.

recursive-factorial-typescript-sdk.title: Recursive Factorial TypeScript SDK
recursive-factorial-typescript-sdk.desc:
This distributed factorial computation showcases the programming model that Resonate prides itself.
	Once you see what is possible, who knows where it will lead you!

kafka-worker-python-sdk.title: Dead Simple Kafka Worker Python SDK
kafka-worker-python-sdk.desc: This template gives you a distributed-worker fleet that consume messages from a Redpanda topic.

worker-load-balancing-typesript-sdk.title: Worker Load Balancing TypeScript SDK
worker-load-balancing-typesript-sdk.desc: This template starts you off with a fleet of workers that are automatically load balanced and recover from failures.

worker-load-balancing-python-sdk.desc: This template starts you off with a fleet of workers that are automatically load balanced and recover from failures.

human-in-the-loop-typescript-sdk.title: Human-In-The Loop TypeScript SDK
human-in-the-loop-typescript-sdk.desc: This template gets you started with a workflow that blocks, waiting for a human to click a link in an email.

website-summarization-agent-python-sdk.title: Website Summarization Agent Python SDK
website-summarization-agent-python-sdk.desc: This template starts you off with a workflow decked out with two failure prone steps, a human-in-the-loop, a non-retriable error, and result caching by ID.
